---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Landscaping Services | Brainard's Greenscapes Las Cruces"
description: "Full-service landscaping in Las Cruces, NM — landscape design, hardscaping, xeriscaping, irrigation, and maintenance. Free on-site estimates."
pageCSS: ["services.css"]
---

<section id="services-500" style="padding-top: clamp(8rem, 14vw, 12rem);">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-picture">
      <img src="/assets/images/brainards-patios-1-1f6f751d.jpeg" alt="Flagstone patio with raised stone planter and lush turf installed by Brainard's Greenscapes" width="500" height="667" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
    </div>
    <div>
      <ul class="cs-card-group">
        {%- for service in services %}
        <li class="cs-item">
          <div class="cs-icon-wrap">
            <img src="{{ service.icon }}" alt="" width="56" height="56" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
          </div>
          <div class="cs-item-body">
            <h2 class="cs-item-title">{{ service.title }}</h2>
            <p class="cs-item-text">{{ service.description }}</p>
            <a href="{{ service.url }}" class="cs-item-link">
              {{ service.linkText }}
              <img src="/assets/svgs/arrow-up-right.svg" alt="" width="14" height="14" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
            </a>
          </div>
        </li>
        {%- endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="process-500">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <ul class="cs-card-group">
      <li class="cs-item">
        <div class="cs-icon-wrap">
          <img src="/assets/svgs/icon-lightbulb-light.svg" alt="" width="40" height="40" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        </div>
        <h3 class="cs-item-title">Free On-Site Consultation</h3>
        <p class="cs-item-text">We walk your property, listen to your vision, and assess sun, soil, and drainage at no cost to you.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="cs-item">
        <div class="cs-icon-wrap">
          <img src="/assets/svgs/icon-lightbulb-light.svg" alt="" width="40" height="40" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        </div>
        <h3 class="cs-item-title">Custom Design &amp; Quote</h3>
        <p class="cs-item-text">You receive a tailored design and itemized proposal built for the Las Cruces climate and your budget.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="cs-item">
        <div class="cs-icon-wrap">
          <img src="/assets/svgs/icon-lightbulb-light.svg" alt="" width="40" height="40" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        </div>
        <h3 class="cs-item-title">Expert Installation</h3>
        <p class="cs-item-text">Our in-house crews handle grading, hardscape, planting, and irrigation on a clear, agreed-upon timeline.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="cs-item">
        <div class="cs-icon-wrap">
          <img src="/assets/svgs/icon-lightbulb-light.svg" alt="" width="40" height="40" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
        </div>
        <h3 class="cs-item-title">Lifetime-Backed Care</h3>
        <p class="cs-item-text">Every project is backed by our workmanship guarantee, with optional seasonal maintenance plans.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <img class="cs-vine cs-vine-1 cs-hide-on-mobile" src="/assets/svgs/leaf-down.svg" alt="" width="88" height="170" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
    <img class="cs-vine cs-vine-2 cs-hide-on-mobile" src="/assets/svgs/leaf-up.svg" alt="" width="88" height="170" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
    <img class="cs-vine cs-vine-3 cs-hide-on-mobile" src="/assets/svgs/leaf-down.svg" alt="" width="88" height="170" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
  </div>
</section>

<section id="lets-talk-318">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <h2 class="cs-title">Let's Talk About Your Landscape</h2>
    <a href="/contact/" class="cs-talk-button">Contact Us</a>
  </div>
  <img class="cs-tree" src="/assets/svgs/talk-tree.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
  <img class="cs-bird cs-bird-1" src="/assets/svgs/talk-bird-1.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
  <img class="cs-bird cs-bird-2" src="/assets/svgs/talk-bird-2.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
  <img class="cs-bird cs-bird-3" src="/assets/svgs/talk-bird-3.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
  <img class="cs-grass" src="/assets/svgs/talk-grass-top.svg" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async">
</section>
